OL,5, Plans to fast-track appeals of hundreds
OL,6, of sub-postmasters affected by the Post
OL,7, Office IT scandal will be announced    
OL,8, "very shortly", a minister said.       
OL,10,FPost Office minister Kevin Hollinrake  
OL,11,Ftold MPs it was investigating ways to  
OL,12,Foverturn convictions, which could      
OL,13,Finclude possible legislation.          
OL,15,FMore than 700 people got criminal      
OL,16,Fconvictions because of faulty software 
OL,17,Fbut only 93 have had them overturned.  
OL,19,FHe indicated more information should be
OL,20,Fgiven by the end of the week.          
